message.content:
cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the preservation of web resources, specifically aggregations of web resources described using Resource Maps (ReMs) from the Object Reuse and Exchange (ORE) project. This topic is closely related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR), as well as cybersecurity (cs.CR) and social networking (cs.SI) due to the use of Web 2.0 services and the involvement of the web community in preservation efforts. Additionally, the use of Resource Maps and the ORE project may also fall under the category of cyberinfrastructure (cs.CY).
